ἡ\">ἡ\u003C/span>  \u003Cbr id=\"al5-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">5\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-text=\"σύμβιος\">σύ[μβ]ιος\u003C/span>  \u003Cspan data-text=\"μνήμης\">μνήμης\u003C/span>  \u003Cbr id=\"al6-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">6\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-text=\"χάριν\">[χ]άριν\u003C/span>  \u003C/span>\u003C/div>  \u003Cp class=\"miniapp\">\u003C/p>\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Marta Fogagnolo\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv id=\"edition-diplomatic\" lang=\"grc\">\u003Cdiv class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\">\u003Cspan class=\"ab\" id=\"div-diplomatic\">\u003Ca id=\"al1-diplomatic\">\u003C!--0-->\u003C/a>\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">1\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-text=\"Θεοῖς\">[..]\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-text=\"Καταχθονίοις\">Κ\u003C/span>\u003Cbr id=\"al2-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">2\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"ος\">\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"ος\">[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>]ΟΣ\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-text=\"ἔζησεν\">ΕΖ[....]\u003C/span>\u003Cbr id=\"al3-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">3\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-text=\"ἔτη\">Ε.[.\u003C/span>\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">·\u003C/span>]Ζ\u003Cspan data-text=\"μῆνες\">ΜΗΝΕ[.\u003C/span>\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>]\u003Cbr id=\"al4-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">4\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-text=\"ἐποίησεν\">ΕΠ[...]ΣΕΝ\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-text=\"αὐτοῦ\">ΑΥΤΟΥ\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-text=\"ἡ\">Η\u003C/span>\u003Cbr id=\"al5-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">5\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-text=\"σύμβιος\">ΣΥ[..]ΙΟΣ\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-text=\"μνήμης\">ΜΝΗΜΗΣ\u003C/span>\u003Cbr id=\"al6-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">6\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-text=\"χάριν\">[.]ΑΡΙΝ\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003C/div>\u003Cp class=\"miniapp\">\u003C/p>\u003C/div>\u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"facsimile-images\">\u003Ch2>Facsimile Images\u003C/h2>\u003Ca href=\"ISic001332_tiled.tif\">\u003Cimg title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana\" src=\"ISic001332_tiled-thumb.tif\">\u003C/a>\u003Ca href=\"ISic001332.jpg\">\u003Cimg title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana\" src=\"ISic001332-thumb.jpg\">\u003C/a>\u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"apparatus\">\u003Ch4>Apparatus criticus\u003C/h4>\u003Cul>\u003Cli>\u003Cspan>\u003Cspan>Text based on photographs\u003C/span>\u003C/span>; \u003C/li>\u003Cli>\u003Cspan>\u003Cspan>Kaibel did not read the first line\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>\u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"translation\">\u003Ch2>English translation\u003C/h2>\u003Cp class=\"translation-author\">\u003Ca href=\"https://orcid.org/0000-0001-5187-5163\">Marta Fogagnolo\u003C/a>\u003C/p>  \u003Cp>To the subterranean deities. ---os lived for -7 years, - months. His wife made (this) for his memory.\u003C/p>  \u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"translation\">\u003Ch2>Italian translation\u003C/h2>\u003Cp class=\"translation-author\">\u003Ca href=\"https://orcid.org/0000-0001-5187-5163\">Marta Fogagnolo\u003C/a>\u003C/p>  \u003Cp>Agli dèi inferi. ---os visse -7 anni, - mesi. Sua moglie realizzò (questo) a sua memoria.\u003C/p>  \u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"commentary\">\u003Ch2>commentary\u003C/h2>  \u003Cp>The epitaph presents the invocation to the subterranean deities, the name of the deceased in the lacuna, the indication of the age (partially in the lacuna) and in another sentence the dedicant (the proper name is not specified, but the relationship with the deceased is mentioned, as in IGMusPalermo 143 = \u003Ca href=\"http://sicily.classics.ox.ac.uk/inscription/ISic000797\" target=\"_blank\">ISic000797\u003C/a>), the dedication verb and the formula \u003Cspan class=\"lang\" lang=\"grc\">μνήμης χάριν\u003C/span>.\u003C/p>  \u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"bibliography\">\u003Ch2>bibliography\u003C/h2>  \u003Cul>\u003Cli>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> Kaibel 1890 \u003Ca href=\"https://clio.columbia.edu/catalog/6873760\" target=\"_blank\">511\u003C/a>  \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001072\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001072\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> Korhonen 2004 155 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000028\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000028\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>  \u003Cul>\u003Cli>\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>  \u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"handnote\">\u003Cp>Letters with serifs: Ε and Σ lunate, Μ cursive.\u003C/p> Lines 1-6  15-20  Interlineation line 1 to 2  not recorded  \u003C/div>\u003Cdiv id=\"license\"> Licensed under a Creative Commons-Attribution 4.0 licence. \u003C/div>",[214,217,220,223,226,228,231,234,237],{"id":215,"html":216},"editions","\u003Cdiv class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Marta Fogagnolo\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv id=\"edition-interpretive\" lang=\"grc\">  \u003Cdiv class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\">\u003Cspan class=\"ab\" id=\"div-interpretive\">  \u003Ca id=\"al1-interpretive\">\u003C!--0-->\u003C/a>\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">1\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-text=\"Θεοῖς\">[Θ(εοῖς)]\u003C/span>  \u003Cspan data-text=\"Καταχθονίοις\">Κ(αταχθονίοις)\u003C/span>  \u003Cbr id=\"al2-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">2\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"ος\">\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"ος\">[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>]ος\u003C/span>\u003C/span>  \u003Cspan data-text=\"ἔζησεν\">ἔζ[ησεν]\u003C/span>  \u003Cbr id=\"al3-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">3\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-tex