>  \u003Cp>The epitaph presents the invocation to the subterranean deities, the name of the deceased in the lacuna, the indication of the age (partially in the lacuna) and in another sentence the dedicant (the proper name is not specified, but the relationship with the deceased is mentioned, as in IGMusPalermo 143 = \u003Ca href=\"http://sicily.classics.ox.ac.uk/inscription/ISic000797\" target=\"_blank\">ISic000797\u003C/a>), the dedication verb and the formula \u003Cspan class=\"lang\" lang=\"grc\">μνήμης χάριν\u003C/span>.\u003C/p>  ",{"id":232,"html":233},"bibliography","\u003Ch2>bibliography\u003C/h2>  \u003Cul>\u003Cli>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> Kaibel 1890 \u003Ca href=\"https://clio.columbia.edu/catalog/6873760\" target=\"_blank\">511\u003C/a>  \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001072\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001072\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> Korhonen 2004 155 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000028\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000028\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>  \u003Cul>\u003Cli>\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>  ",{"id":235,"html":236},"handnote","\u003Cp>Letters with serifs: Ε and Σ lunate, Μ cursive.\u003C/p> Lines 1-6  15-20  Interlineation line 1 to 2  not recorded  ",{"id":238,"html":239},"license"," Licensed under a Creative Commons-Attribution 4.0 licence. ",[241,243,246,247],{"html":242},"Text encoding: Marta Fogagnolo",{"id":244,"lang":123,"html":245},"edition-interpretive","\u003Cdiv class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\">\u003Cspan class=\"ab\" id=\"div-interpretive\">  \u003Ca id=\"al1-interpretive\">\u003C!--0-->\u003C/a>\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">1\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-text=\"Θεοῖς\">[Θ(εοῖς)]\u003C/span>  \u003Cspan data-text=\"Καταχθονίοις\">Κ(αταχθονίοις)\u003C/span>  \u003Cbr id=\"al2-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">2\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"ος\">\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\